<h2 id="the-secret-behind-getuser">The Secret Behind getUser() <a class="headerlink" href="the-user-object#the-secret-behind-getuser" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>But you know I hate secrets: I want to know what that <code>getUser()</code> method <em>really</em>
does. So hold <code>Command</code> and <code>click</code> to see that method.</p>
